## Ticket Integration

### Quick Findings

```bash
# File feature ideas
bobby create -t "Title" --type feature --area dashboard

# File bugs
bobby create -t "Title" --type bug -p high --area auth

# File improvements
bobby create -t "Title" --type improvement --area onboarding
```

### After a Review

Always produce:
1. **Screenshot evidence** — capture current state
2. **Summary of findings** organized by severity
3. **Filed tickets** for every actionable finding

### Quick Reference

```bash
# View board
bobby list

# View specific stage
bobby list backlog
bobby list building

# Move tickets
bobby move TKT-XXX plan       # backlog -> planning
bobby move TKT-XXX block "Needs product decision"

# Comment on ticket
bobby comment TKT-XXX --by bobby-pm "PM review: summary"
```

